{"tid":1610321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香 港 公 共 醫 療 醫 生 協 會 譴 責 警 察 蓄 意 射 傷 市 民","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:06:57.000Z","uid":219007,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4c1d7a87c9ae2291bf79299bbb286ffc246f92","tid":1610321,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71685032_2447744038678264_7362911080332394496_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_oc=AQlvKe3yIYRdaUAIJwQZFQyZe1V_Usb9uG8s9ua-KTBpsmgi4xLWmDbACFXMZAPrQ1U&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=ea0c45d57e04063793fc1daaa9a7d47e&amp;oe=5E39B68D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71685032_2447744038678264_7362911080332394496_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_oc%3DAQlvKe3yIYRdaUAIJwQZFQyZe1V_Usb9uG8s9ua-KTBpsmgi4xLWmDbACFXMZAPrQ1U%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dea0c45d57e04063793fc1daaa9a7d47e%26oe%3D5E39B68D&h=2ef80e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKPDA.publicdoctors/photos/a.856286314490719/2447744032011598/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKPDA.publicdoctors%2Fphotos%2Fa.856286314490719%2F2447744032011598%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=75c2e756\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKPDA.publicdoctors/photos/a.856286314490719/2447744032011598/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"253b7c09bdcf27aa77d3f5ba49e2c9649ee9a7a7","tid":1610321,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beca0b2f636f5e7f7636fd2437ad021a180cde0a","tid":1610321,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8417d497d7068dd055852ad9016a4412c154aee6","tid":1610321,"uid":219007,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"香港公共醫療醫生協會譴責警察蓄意射傷市民<br />\n<br />\n本會強烈譴責香港警察使用過份武力清場，開槍嚴重傷害示威者。<br />\n<br />\n警方於今天下午四時在荃灣海壩街一帶進行清場期間，近距離開槍射擊一名中五學生。從網上影片所見，開槍警員只是被棍攻擊手部，並沒有如警方辯稱生命受到嚴重威脅。學生中槍旋即倒地並大量出血，傷者同伴見狀，立刻上前試圖施救，惟被另一名防暴警察阻止並將之制服按在地上。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">開槍警員在射擊前沒有對示威者發出口頭警告，即於極近距離對準致命部位開槍。除此以外，該名警員當時左手手執一支用作發射布袋彈的長槍，然而警員選擇以殺傷力更大的手槍向學生左胸瞄準發射，而並非以殺傷力低級的布袋彈向非致命身體部位發射。 警員行徑根本與行刑無異， 亦嚴重超出警隊應該使用的武力水平，本會予以強烈譴責。事後，警方在社交媒體表示相關學生只是膊頭位置附近受傷，而非左邊胸腔受槍傷，嚴重歪曲事實。</span><br />\n<br />\n社會各界人士過往已多次提出，在雙方武力不對等的情況下，警方並沒有跟從指引，以最低武力去制服示威者。<span style=\"color: red;\">前線警員對市民、記者、醫護人員懷有敵意，毫不尊重香港市民的示威和基本權利。可是，警方高層不但沒檢討下屬隊表現，而且多次替其過失辯解。</span><br />\n<br />\n示威運動六月至今，政府從未釋出認真解決本港政治問題的意向，只以武力試圖消滅一代香港年輕人，這只能令香港的情況不斷退後。 <span style=\"color: red;\">如此行為，敗盡警隊多年來建立的專業形象，不但令更多香港市民蒙受不必要的傷害，將香港警察推到市民的對立面, 更嚴重損害香港的國際形象。</span><br />\n<br />\n本會祝願所有傷者盡快康復。<br />\n<br />\n香港公共醫療醫生協會<br />\n二〇一九年十月一日"},{"pid":"ad188ae1abc92863391951f93904bbbecaa166e8","tid":1610321,"uid":185872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"507a5cfd546579bc5e9f630b254178d985f840fc","tid":1610321,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ec4aaaff97b5b228de84c1cc95eb61aaf86db0","tid":1610321,"uid":136233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"284e5b33cb813ac0f4cf195bdeb8f81c38fd3dde","tid":1610321,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:08:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ac20ed55a9e552397c5aeda92ad74646e5fbf16","tid":1610321,"uid":280058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:09:30.000Z","msg":"黑警嬲既話記得有病唔好睇醫生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\